- **Title:** Carrick Therapeutics Announces U.S. FDA Clearance of IND for CT7439, a First-In-Class Inhibitor of CDK12/13  
  **URL:** `https://www.globenewswire.com/fr/news-release/2023/09/07/2739242/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-U-S-FDA-Clearance-of-IND-for-CT7439-a-First-In-Class-Inhibitor-of-CDK12-13.html` ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/fr/news-release/2023/09/07/2739242/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-U-S-FDA-Clearance-of-IND-for-CT7439-a-First-In-Class-Inhibitor-of-CDK12-13.html?utm_source=openai))  
  **Direct quote snippets:**
  - “Investigational New Drug (IND) application for **CT7439**, a novel cyclin dependent kinase 12/13 (**CDK12/13**) inhibitor.” ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/fr/news-release/2023/09/07/2739242/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-U-S-FDA-Clearance-of-IND-for-CT7439-a-First-In-Class-Inhibitor-of-CDK12-13.html?utm_source=openai))  
  - “advanced solid tumors, including **breast**, **ovarian** and **Ewing's Sarcoma**.” ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/fr/news-release/2023/09/07/2739242/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-U-S-FDA-Clearance-of-IND-for-CT7439-a-First-In-Class-Inhibitor-of-CDK12-13.html?utm_source=openai))  

- **Title:** Carrick Therapeutics Announces First Patient Dosed in Phase 1 Clinical Trial of CT7439 (CDK12/13 Inhibitor)  
  **URL:** `https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/09/23/2951333/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-First-Patient-Dosed-in-Phase-1-Clinical-Trial-of-CT7439-CDK12-13-Inhibitor.html` ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/09/23/2951333/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-First-Patient-Dosed-in-Phase-1-Clinical-Trial-of-CT7439-CDK12-13-Inhibitor.html?utm_source=openai))  
  **Direct quote snippets:**
  - “evaluating **CT7439**, a novel cyclin dependent kinase 12/13 (**CDK12/13**) inhibitor / **Cyclin-K glue-degrader**.” ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/09/23/2951333/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-First-Patient-Dosed-in-Phase-1-Clinical-Trial-of-CT7439-CDK12-13-Inhibitor.html?utm_source=openai))  
  - “study ID: **NCT06600789**.” ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/09/23/2951333/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-First-Patient-Dosed-in-Phase-1-Clinical-Trial-of-CT7439-CDK12-13-Inhibitor.html?utm_source=openai))  

- **Title:** FDA Clears IND Application for First-in-Class CDK12/13 Inhibitor  
  **URL:** `https://www.cancernetwork.com/view/fda-clears-ind-application-for-first-in-class-cdk12-13-inhibitor` ([cancernetwork.com](https://www.cancernetwork.com/view/fda-clears-ind-application-for-first-in-class-cdk12-13-inhibitor?utm_source=openai))  
  **Direct quote snippets:**
  - “**CDK12/13 inhibitor CT7439**” ([cancernetwork.com](https://www.cancernetwork.com/view/fda-clears-ind-application-for-first-in-class-cdk12-13-inhibitor?utm_source=openai))  
  - “**breast cancer**, **ovarian cancer**, and **Ewing’s sarcoma**.” ([cancernetwork.com](https://www.cancernetwork.com/view/fda-clears-ind-application-for-first-in-class-cdk12-13-inhibitor?utm_source=openai))  

- **Title:** Syros Presents New Preclinical Data on its CDK12 Inhibitor Program at American Association for Cancer Research (AACR) Annual Meeting 2022  
  **URL:** `https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20220408005014/en/Syros-Presents-New-Preclinical-Data-on-its-CDK12-Inhibitor-Program-at-American-Association-for-Cancer-Research-AACR-Annual-Meeting-2022` ([businesswire.com](https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20220408005014/en/Syros-Presents-New-Preclinical-Data-on-its-CDK12-Inhibitor-Program-at-American-Association-for-Cancer-Research-AACR-Annual-Meeting-2022?utm_source=openai))  
  **Direct quote snippets:**
